content: Just got back from the AI ethics conference, had some great discussions. Xander's AI now has a better understanding of long-term ethical impacts. Emily and I had a cozy dinner with homemade vegan dishes.

Xander's trading model now considers environmental impact. Emily and I explored this old shipyard, got some creepy vibes for our vlog. Got an email from a DeFi protocol interested in our ethical trading approach.
Had a productive day, Xander's AI now has a social media engagement framework in testing. Emily and I finalized our rooftop garden plans. Got some pushback on my AI ethics paper, time to revise.

Xander's AI is now more autonomous in decision-making, but there's a new challenge with resource management. Emily and I had a fun day exploring hidden spots in Brooklyn. Preparing for my DeFi conference talk.
